title: Exception throws when exporting data from table containing highlight/map
description: When exporting data from the attached report, an exception is thrown.
OB: An exception is thrown when attempting to export data from a table that contains a highlight rule and a map rule in the group row.
EB: No exception should be thrown when exporting data from a table that contains a highlight rule and a map rule in the group row.
SR:
To reproduce the exception:
1. Add a table to the report that has a group, a highlight rule, and a map rule in the group row.
2. Preview the report.
3. Export the data from the table.
